{
  "stem": "8786.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took him into a town, which is called Rozno, which is a border town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And naturally, they were paid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they told him, we know that you are Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the way the men spoke to us, we just couldn't say no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is my father's style in talking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were marching into a forest of this of Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Koller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Koller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Koller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "K-O-L-L-E-R.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He died after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was a very ambitious, big businessmen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was an army officer in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They ran into the forest, and they stayed in the forest hiding in the Slovakian forest in the-- I wouldn't say the name, because I'm not so sure how it was spelled.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think not far from the Carpathian for three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "December, January, and February.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were staying in the cold, cold in the woods up high mountains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were many times in big danger because they heard the Germans with dogs looking for partisans in the Slovakian forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is a different story, what happened in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And thank goodness they did survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They had to go out every second.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Third day, they went out to a little farm, picked up this some food, bought something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They had-- so a chicken they picked or somebody-- somebody, one of them picked it up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they lived it through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was not easy, because it was cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And by the time when he came home, his eyes were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] affected from the-- there was a lot of smoke.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They couldn't make a big fire because it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "However, there was a smokey little fire to keep them warm enough.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
